* **Be Part of Research**: `https://bepartofresearch.nihr.ac.uk/`
* **Health Research Authority (HRA)**: `https://www.hra.nhs.uk/`
* **NHS Supply Chain**: `https://www.supplychain.nhs.uk/`
* **NHS Shared Business Services**: `https://www.sbs.nhs.uk/`
* **NHS Blood and Transplant**: `https://www.nhsbt.nhs.uk/`
* **NHS Blood Donation**: `https://www.blood.co.uk/`
